related_questions.question: How much money can you make as a travel agent?
related_questions.snippet: Host Agency Reviews and the Bureau of Labor Statistics (BLS) found some common ground in regard to the average salary of a travel agent. The BLS currently lists the average travel agent salary in 2017 as $40,840 with a range of $21,350 and $62,320 dividing the lower to upper 10% of travel agents.Feb 5, 2019

related_questions.question: Where do travel agents work?
related_questions.snippet: Travel agents work in an office environment where they spend much of their time on the phone. They typically work in offices, but some work remotely because much of their time is spent on the phone and the computer.
